data.description: Rustic Cabin on View Lot with extra Shop space. Enjoy the View from this cozy home in the forest. 3 Bedroom and 2 Bath with a 2car Garage. The home is in a great community with no Restrictions and no HOA. Tranquil Acres has access to the ATV Trails available north of the area. Wood Stove in the Living room keeps the warmth in the snow and a great wood deck to absorb the sun. Detached Garage with room for a shop. Two Sheds on the property that have electricity. Great community and a great cabin, come see it now...
